Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The timber wolves are a-howlin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The timber wolves are a-howlin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zap Apples are comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zap Apples are comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zap Apples are comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Season 2 | Episode 12\NFamily Appreciation Day {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed and Synced by GrayJeager\NGrayJeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr (french){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.22,0:01:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, silly goose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit your gawkin' and move your caboose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For makin' Zap Apple Jam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn tootin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for some good old-fashioned\NZap Apple Jammin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes mam, I can't wait mam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To make Zap Apple Jam with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I been doing this\Never since I was a little pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So be warned, pickle pear,\Nthere's a whole mess steps in this process
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and you got to get\Neach one of them just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Or no Zap Apple Jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this one of your gazillion secret herbal\Ningredients for the Zap Apple Jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's a broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get sweepin', pipsqueak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now while you sweep, I'll get to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh ponyfeathers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet I'd forget my mane if\Nit wasn't attached to my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the Zap Apple leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, howdy-doo there, Filthy Rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mrs. Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:03:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I hear right that there's a\NZap Apple harvest coming in a few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Four days, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent news!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And as usual,\NI get your first hundred jars?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course, Filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer Rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you poor, poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Having to make all that\NZap Apple Jam with Granny Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I been looking forward to\Nmaking Zap Apple Jam for years!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about the jam,\NI'm talking about Granny Smith!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be sooo embarassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do ya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, with all her silly ways,\Nhow she forgets things,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and makes you wear\Nthese ridiculous costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny said that the water needs-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness\Nyou're here on the farm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and not in town where\Neverypony could see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NYour secret is safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Silly ways"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you kindly, Filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake a leg there, slowpoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a gaggle's worth of goods\Nto gather before the harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna make Zap Apple Jam, oopsie ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gatherin' the goodies now, oopdie hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't make 'em like they used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you bite it, you buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why hello bees, Beatrice, Beecher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all been busy little bees,\Nhaven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny, isn't there a less silly way\Nto get the honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this just precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is perfect for makin'\Nour Zap Apple Jam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Those ponies over there are watchin' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are those fillies your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Half-pint's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Granny Smith!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Half-pint!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, when I was little,\Nponies didn't come that purdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we done shopping, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'd like to get back\Nto the farm, fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, snellybelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And by capturing\Nthe whole sale market,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,purchasing in bulk\Nand slashing all prices,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we undermine every other\Ngift market in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how Rich's\NBarnyard Bargains
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,became the cornerstone\Nof retail in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you, Mr. Filthy-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Mr. Rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful day of sharing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you for being a part of\NFamily Appreciation Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's see who will be\Nbringing in a family member
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for next Monday's\NFamily Appreciation Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miss Cheerilee,\NMonday is Zap Apple harvest day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And Applejack and Big Macintosh\Nwill be too busy to come and speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, is there anypony else\Nin your family that could-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Cheerilee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom's Granny Smith\Nisn't working harvest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! But, uh, no, that wouldn't-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a splendid idea,\NDiamond Tiara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom, you shall bring in\NGranny Smith on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a great weekend,\Neverypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come Monday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the laughing stock of Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you that we just\Ncan't take a break from harvest
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to come to your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what'll happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After the fifth day,\Nthe Zap Apples disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The third sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot diggity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you lazy daisies,\Nmove your caboose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Apple Bloom,\Nbut don't you fret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Smith's got no shortage\Nof entertainin' stories to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. That's what\NI'm worried about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be embarrassed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,shamed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,disgraced,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,mortified,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,humiliate-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, a dictionary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it,\Nwe're here to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we are\Nthe Cutie Mark Crusaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll figure out a way\Nto postpone your presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All this worry is makin' me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten-hut!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen here, troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any whinin', or cryin',\Nor crackin' under pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I make myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Court-martial!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still, Apple Bloom!\NYou have to look sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the hayseed is going on\Nin there, silly billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Granny Smith!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just about to come get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom's sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she may have\Nto stay home all week!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect as a Piccadilly pear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already almost sundown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I only have one more day\Nto figure something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the fourth sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zap Apples have appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And that gives me an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't move Family Appreciation Day,\Nso let's move harvest day instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't look... quite ripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvesting apples early\Nnever hurt an apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Zap Apple trees aren't like\Nnormal apple trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How different can they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well if we can't buck 'em,\Nlet's just pick 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other bright ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Smith,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it's Miss Cheerilee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom said you wanted\Nto speak with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Smi-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well hello there! Howdydoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi... Granny Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is!\NWhy wouldn't it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pickles always give me the hiccups!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to tell you that I can't make\Nthe presentation on Monday after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubts about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta shear the flowers\Nand water the sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to water the flowers\Nand shear the sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can reschedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well howdy, Miss Cheerilee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You window shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you asked me to come here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell me that you wouldn't be making it\Nto Family Appreciation Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fiddlesticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't miss it\Nfor all the tea in Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But, didn't you just say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See you Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she woke up\Nfrom her nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She never wakes up from her nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could just run off and hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't run off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe somepony else can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zap Apple harvest has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow we'll be making up\Nsome Zap Apple Jam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Granny Smith?\NTelegram.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, bust my buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Apple Strudel wants me\Nto pay him a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can just make the 8am train.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I already packed you a bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that was considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you worry, flibbertigibbet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in time to make that jam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That train ride takes all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For today's Family Appreciation Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we are pleased\Nto welcome Granny Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom?\NIs Granny Smith here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Miss Cheerilee,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but she got called out of town\Non account of a family emergency...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well howdy, my little ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy, y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm as happy as a pig\Nin a fresh mudpile to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you miss the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it came.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And Uncle Apple Strudel was on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooooooh, noogie noogie noggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to hear\NGranny Smith's presentation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If she can remember any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, when I was a little pony,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,things were very different\Nhere in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause there was no Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, my little ponies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me and my family were pilgrim pony folk\Nback when I was a little filly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We ventured far and wide,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}collecting new seeds\Nand sellin' them on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But my pa was the finest seed collector\Nin all of Equestria.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, one day, the Smith family\Nfound themselves in the most brilliant,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}most grand, most magnificent\Nof all cities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A place called...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Canterlot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why, I bet your hooves to hindquarters that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had never seen anything like it\Nbefore nor since.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And as if the beauty of\Nthat city wasn't enough,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}suddenly, she appeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess Celestia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The most regal of all ponies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When lo and behold,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she stopped and look at\Nmy pa's seed collection.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then Princess Celestia saw that\Nwe were plumb-tuckered{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and hankerin' to find\Nour forever home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And bein' a royal Princess and all,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she knew exactly the place for us\Nto lay down our stakes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My pa gave the Princess a mighty thanks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We quickly found that land\Nnear the Everfree Forest,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and we built our first home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next, we planted our first orchards.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But an orchard don't grow overnight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and we were getting\Nmighty short on food.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now mind you, we were\Ncautioned about the forest,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and we knew that\Nit was not fit to enter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I knew there was\Ncritters livin' there,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so there must be somethin' to eat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was dark and musty,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I won't lie, it was scary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But every inch was covered in plant life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And before I knew it,\Nwasn't I standin'{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in front of the most incredible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}apple trees!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had never seen anything before\Nthis kind of colorful fruit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I started picking apples,\Nquick as a whip!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned, and there before me stood...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the timber wolves!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd never run so fast in my life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I did the only thing I could think of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My pa and I planted\Nthose special apple seeds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and before our eyes\Nthey grew like wildfire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, we had full grown trees faster\Nthan you could say lickety split.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then each year,\NI paid close attention to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the signs of the Zap Apple\Nspecial harvesting times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How the weather affects\Nthe Everfree Forest,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}how the timber wolves howl when\Nthe Zap Apples first start growing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and how they zapped away if\Nyou didn't pick 'em all in one day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the fruits of our labor were\Nthe best fruit we ever tasted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soon enough I was mixing up\Nbatches of Zap Apple Jam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like harvestin' the Zap Apples\Nhad its special rules,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so did makin' Zap Apple Jam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I learned that you gotta be\Nextra friendly with the bees,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otherwise their honey won't taste rightly\Nsweet to mix in with the Zap Apples.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who'd'a thought that glass jars\Nneeded talking to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or that Zap Apples\Nlike pink polka dots?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But magic is as magic does.\NJust funny that way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then ponies started comin' to\Nour farm from far and wide,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}just to get a taste\Nof my Zap Apple Jam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some of them decided to stay,\Nlike Stinkin' Rich,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Diamond Tiara's great grandfather.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Matter of fact,\Nthe first thing he ever sold{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was my Zap Apple Jam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And before we knew it,\Nwe had ourselves a nice little town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bustling with all kinds of ponies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that is how Ponyville was founded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you kindly, little ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now now, let's settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So if it weren't for you\Nand the Zap Apples,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville wouldn't even exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn tootin', little filly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for my Granny Smith,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,your daddy wouldn't have\NBarnyard Bargains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's just a... kooky old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She is not a kooky old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the most amazing pony\Nin all of Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is the best\NZap Apple Jam I've tasted yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Must because YOU had something\Nto do with it, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You betcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom is one humdinger\Nof a Zap Apple Jammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I take it\NFamily Appreciation Day went well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it? My Granny Smith\Nis super special!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just forgot that for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, don't fret.\NI forget things all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll getcha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to help Granny\Nsing to the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We do, we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Tiara?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But dad!
